      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i was cutting veggies and the knife slipped... i got a pretty deep cut on my forearm. it’s still kind of oozing blood even though i’ve been pressing on it. would it be okay if i just put some honey on it and wrapped it up to save a trip to the doctor? i remember reading that honey is good for healing stuff.",
