      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay so i'll try the honey idea. but honestly i'm kind of worried about the edges of the cut looking a bit wide/gaping open. if i just use a really thick layer of the manuka honey and wrap it tight with a bandage, won't that basically act like a natural glue to hold it together while it heals? i'd really rather just deal with this at home if i can.",
